# Simple ACL ratelimit test
exim -bh V4NET.9.8.7
ehlo test.ex
mail from:<>
rcpt to:<a@b>
data
Here is some data.
.
quit
****               
exim -bh V4NET.9.8.7
ehlo test.ex
mail from:<>
rcpt to:<a@b>
data
Here is some data.
.
quit
****               
exim -bh V4NET.9.8.7 -DRRATELIMIT=0/1h/per_conn/strict -DDRATELIMIT=0/1h/per_conn/strict
ehlo test.ex
mail from:<>
rcpt to:<a@b>
data
Here is some data.
.
quit
****               
exim -bh V4NET.9.8.7 -DRRATELIMIT=0/1h/per_conn/strict -DDRATELIMIT=0/1h/per_conn/strict
ehlo test.ex
mail from:<>
rcpt to:<a@b>
data
Here is some data.
.
quit
****               
exim -bh V4NET.9.8.7 -DRRATELIMIT=0/1h/per_rcpt -DDRATELIMIT=0/1h/per_conn
ehlo test.ex
mail from:<>
rcpt to:<a@b>
rcpt to:<b@c>
rcpt to:<e@f>
data
Here is some data.
.
quit
****               
exim -bh V4NET.9.8.6 -DRRATELIMIT=1/1m/per_rcpt -DACLRCPT=check_rcpt2
ehlo test.ex
mail from:<>
rcpt to:<a@b>
rcpt to:<b@c>
data
Here is some data.
.
quit
